I think the standard is to use LSL A (same with LSR, ROL, ROR, and for 65C02 processors INC and DEC).<br /><br />LSL alone looks like an incomplete instruction to me.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Sun Dec 08, 2013 7:33 am</p><hr />
